Revision history for App-Geshtinanna

0.0.1   (unreleased)
        - Initial sketch of the Suricata ingest pipeline.
        - App::Geshtinanna::Config: load /usr/local/etc/geshtinanna.toml.
        - App::Geshtinanna::Suricata: POE + POE::Wheel::FollowTail engine that
          tails Suricata EVE flow logs and feeds each event into a Zorita set
          (batch Writer or online streaming Client), with flow/http/dns/tls
          extractors.
        - App::Geshtinanna::SetInfo: install shipped set prototypes as Zorita
          sets (prototype -> info.json bridge).
        - App::Geshtinanna::CLI / geshtinanna: App::Cmd front end.
        - share/set_info_jsons split into online/ and batch/ prototypes;
          maint/online2batch.pl derives the batch twins from the online ones.
